Package: scalecard
Type: Package
Title: Rectify and Scale Photographs Using the Credit Card Photography Scale
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ioannis", "Daliakopoulos", email = "idaliak@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Perspective-corrects ("rectifies") and scales photographs taken with
    the Credit Card Photography Scale (Past Horizons) calibration card. The card's
    three crosshair rectification targets (on a 50 x 20 mm frame), red/yellow/blue
    colour patches and 8 cm scale-bar squares are detected automatically and used
    as ground-control points for a projective (homography) transform, producing a
    flat image at a known pixels-per-millimetre scale. Optional white-balance and
    colour-correction off the card's reference swatches are provided. This is an R
    port of a browser (OpenCV.js) tool, built on 'magick', 'imager' and 'EBImage'
    instead of OpenCV.
